---
title: Haloumi & Roast Veggie Traybake with Capers & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: There was complete mayhem when this dish hit our tasting table. With a medley of sweet roasted veggies mixed up in gooey, salty haloumi, plus a herbed mayo dolloped on top, it disappeared from the bowl in record time.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/haloumi-roast-veggie-traybake-dc12ee06.jpg
